# Monorepo Structure

This is a **100% TypeScript monorepo**. Every package, app, and library MUST be written entirely in TypeScript.

## Package Types

| Type | Path | Tooling | Example |
|------|------|---------|---------|
| React web app | `apps/<name>-web/` | Rsbuild | `apps/dashboard-web/` |
| NestJS server | `apps/<name>-server/` | NestJS CLI | `apps/auth-server/` |
| Shared library | `libs/<name>/` | tsc | `libs/shared-types/` |

## Naming Conventions

- Package names: `@primer-guidy/<name>` (kebab-case)
- Web apps suffix: `-web`
- Server apps suffix: `-server`
- Shared libs live in `libs/`

## Constraints

- NO JavaScript files (`.js`, `.jsx`) — TypeScript only (`.ts`, `.tsx`)
- Every package MUST have its own `tsconfig.json` extending root config
- Strict TypeScript: `strict: true` always enabled
- NO `any` type — use `unknown` and narrow with type guards
- Shared types/interfaces go in `libs/shared-types/`
